    <body>
      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="X49-362H">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-X49-362H-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X49-362H-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X49-362H-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">Written with a design to be spoken by her, on his arrivat at Glassnevin.&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-X49-362H-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X49-362H-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X49-362H-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">Doctor Delany having Complimented him with a House there.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X49-362H-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X49-362H-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X49-362H-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-1" n="1">Tho' the Name of this Place may make you to frown,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-2" n="2">Your Deanship is welcome to <hi rend="italics">Glass ne vin</hi> Town;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-3" n="3">A Glass and no Wine, to a Man of your Taste,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-4" n="4">Alass! is enough to break it in haste:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-5" n="5">Be that as it will, your presence can't fail,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-6" n="6">To yield great delight in drinking our Ale;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-7" n="7">Would you but vouchsafe a Mug to partake,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-8" n="8">And, as we can Brew, believe we can Bake.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-9" n="9">The Life, and the Pleasure, we now from you hope, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-10" n="10">The fam'd Violante can't Show on the Rope;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-11" n="11">\<hi rend="italics">hole</hi>\ts out-do, even Pope.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-12" n="12">Then wh\<hi rend="italics">hole</hi>\ at Glassnevin and find,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-13" n="13">The benefit wish'd you by Friends who are kind;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-14" n="14">One Night in the Week your favour bestow,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-15" n="15">To drink with Delany, and others you know:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-16" n="16">They constantly meet, at Peg Rat Cliff's, together,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-17" n="17">Talk over the News of the Town, and the Weather;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-18" n="18">Reflect on Mishaps, in Church and in State, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-19" n="19">Digest many things, as well as good Meat;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-20" n="20">And Club each alike, that no one may treat.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-21" n="21">This, if you will grant, without Coach, or a Chair,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-22" n="22">You may in a trice, cross the way, and be there;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-23" n="23">For Peg is your Neighbour, as well as Delany,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X49-362H-line-24" n="24">\<hi rend="italics">hole</hi>\Housewifely Woman, full pleasing to many.</l>
          </lg>
